'''Nhazz''' was an alien member of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. In [[10 ABY/Legends|10 ABY]], his brother was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] hauling cargo for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], and present at the [[Byss Bistro]].

